Rousseau was born at [[Namur]] on 14 January 1887 and died there on 7 September 1981.<ref>[http://catalogue.bnf.fr/servlet/autorite?ID=11988110&idNoeud=1.2&host=catalogue BnF catalogue général]</ref>
