'''''Tarombo''''' is a term for '[[genealogy]]' in [[Batak (Indonesia)|Batak]] culture/language.<ref>{{cite book|author=B. K. Marpaung|title=Buku Pusaka Tarombo Batak|year=1954|publisher=Raja|oclc=559425}}</ref> The Batak believe that they all come from the same ancestor: [[Siraja Batak]], the Batak Patriarch.<ref>{{cite book|author=Jan S. Aritonang|title=Mission Schools in Batakland (Indonesia): 1861–1940|year=1994|publisher=BRILL|isbn=90-04-09967-0}}</ref> They kept the genealogy line tracing back to this ancestor, called [http://www.tarombobatak.com Tarombo Batak]. Its origins however have been clouded with legends.
